Program: Discovery
Title: Was there life on Mars?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwvh
Last Broadcast Date: 27 March 1997
Was there ever life on Mars? The Lunar and Planetary Science Conference has debated the discovery of a meteorite from Mars which contained fossilised evidence of life. Also in the programme a look at diseases which attack the immune system and why they are more prevalent in developed nations. Plus, inside the mind of a London cab driver. Presenter: Martin Redfern. Show less